text: The Aegon Eastbourne Trophy was a tournament for professional female tennis players played on outdoor grass courts. The event was classified as a $50,000 ITF Women's Circuit tournament and was held in Eastbourne, United Kingdom, from 2015 to 2016. == Past finals == === Singles === {|class="wikitable" style="font-size:90%" |- !Year !width="200"|Champion !width="200"|Runner-up !width="175"|Score |- | 2016 || Alison Riske || Tara Moore || 4–6, 7–6(7–5), 6–3 |- | 2015 || Anett Kontaveit || Alla Kudryavtseva || 7–6(7–4), 7–6(7–2) |} === Doubles === {|class="wikitable" style="font-size:90%" |- !Year !width="200"|Champions !width="200"|Runners-up !width="175"|Score |- | 2016 || Yang Zhaoxuan Zhang Kailin || Asia Muhammad Maria Sanchez || 7–6(7–5), 6–1 |- | 2015 || Shelby Rogers Coco Vandeweghe || Jocelyn Rae Anna Smith || 7–5, 7–6(7–1) |} == External links == * ITF search * Official Website Category:ITF Women's Circuit Category:Grass court tennis tournaments Category:Tennis tournaments in the United Kingdom Category:Recurring sporting events established in 2015 Category:Recurring sporting events disestablished in 2016 Category:2015 establishments in the United Kingdom Category:Defunct tennis tournaments in the United Kingdom
